{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_07_02",
  "title": "白石沙季 2話 自分に足りないもの",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "やっと戻ってきたか。ええと……沙季、大丈夫か？\nさっきから様子が変だぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Finally back‚ huh. Um… Saki‚ are you okay?\nYou've seemed off since earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "……こほん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Cough",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "問題などありません。練習はつつがなく進んでいます\n――全ては絶対勝利のために",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No problems at all. Practice is going smoothly…\n――All for the sake of absolute victory.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6666678112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "沙季……かわいそうに……疲れてるんだな\n明日の予定、調整しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki… I feel bad for you… You must be tired.\nLet's adjust tomorrow's schedule.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4973469696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！？\n私、疲れておかしくなった訳じゃないですよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!?\nI-I'm not tired to the point of being weird‚ okay!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ～……本人だと様になっているのに\nどうして私が真似すると決まらないんでしょうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… even though it looks okay when it's them‚\nwhy doesn't it work when I try to imitate them…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.499996694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして今のは……スリクスの真似をしてたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be… you were imitating IIIX just now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.8183450026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "はい……kanaさんとmihoさんの口調を\n真似てました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… I was mimicking kana-san and\nmiho-san's speech.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2000017803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスのライブ映像を観ていて思ったんです\n彼女達には強烈な個性があるんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While watching IIIX's live footage‚ I thought\nthey have such strong individuality.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9333351136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ映像からだけでは伝わらない、スリクスを\nスリクスたらしめているものを探ろうと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to find what makes ⅢX being ⅢX\nwhich is not shown on live footage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6666679383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどなぁ……いつもの分析とはまた違う\nアプローチに挑戦したって訳か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… You're challenging yourself with different approach\nwith your usual analysis.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.499996376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、franさんのような立ち方や歩き方も\n心掛けてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I'm also paying attention to\nfran-san's posture and walking style.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7666679383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "だからいつも以上に姿勢がいいのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that's why your posture seems even better than usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4813835108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "あとは株の変動を見守っていますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm also keeping an eye on stock market fluctuations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.5147168442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そこも真似してるのか……。沙季、言いにくいんだが\n最近スリクスから苦情がきてたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're mimicking that too… Saki‚ it's hard to say‚ but\nrecently‚ IIIX has been complaining.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.4253328924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "えっ。く、苦情ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? C-complaining?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.325333401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "「沙季がやたらじろじろ見てくる\nなんとかしてくれないか」……ってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Saki keeps staring at us‚ can you do something about it?\"…\nSomething like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6725671893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "私、そんなに怪しく見えてたんですか！？\nうぅ……申し訳ないですし、ショックです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did I really look that suspicious!?\nUgh… I'm sorry and… shocked…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.8333412172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか前も似たようなことがあったな……\nそうだ、千紗だ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ something similar happened before…\nThat's right‚ with Chisa!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.0434332656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "え？　千紗……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Chisa…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.143428688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "千紗が大人びた雰囲気に憧れてスリクスを尾行したり\n真似をしたことがあったんだよ。やっぱり姉妹なんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa once admired IIIX and even followed\nand imitated them. You guys are really like sisters.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.6203899033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、千紗の様子がおかしかった時がありました\nあの子と同じことをしてしまうなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ there was a time when Chisa's behavior was strange.\nDoing the same things as her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.9666745506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あまり根を詰めると分析もうまくいかないだろ？\n無理はしないでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Analyzing too intensely might not work out well‚ you know?\nDon't push yourself too hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2440860081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "ですが……時間は限られていますし\n思いついたことはなんでもやらないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… time is limited‚ and I feel like I have to try\neverything that comes to mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.2666745506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "私には……それくらいしか取り柄がありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because… that's the only thing I'm good at…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.9925890256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "沙季……なんだかいつもより焦ってないか？\nどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki… you seem more anxious than usual.\nWhat's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.9644708921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスの皆さんを観察していて分かったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While observing IIIX‚ I realized something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.1644708921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "私と彼女達の間には……\nどうしようもないくらい才能の差があるんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's an undeniable gap in talent\nbetween them and me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.1666745506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスのグループ練習を見た時\n何よりもその短さに驚いたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I saw their group practice‚\nwhat surprised me the most was its brevity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.3666735334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "雑談もなく、ごく短時間で仕上げて、あっという間に\n帰ってしまう……月ストの練習とは全然違いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No small talk‚ just finishing in a very short time and then…\nThey just left… It was completely different from Moon Tempest's practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.6666735334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "私は自主練習をしてからグループ練習に臨んで\n寮に帰ったら練習の映像を見て復習しています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I practice on my own before group sessions and\nreview footage when I return to the dorm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.4333310447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "けれど、スリクスの皆さんは\nそんな風にしていないようでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it seemed like\nIIIX doesn't do it that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "確かにスリクスは練習時間が相当短い。星見プロに\n限らず、アイドル業界全体を見てもめずらしいだろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed‚ IIIX has significantly shorter practice times.\nIt's unusual not only within Hoshimi Prods‚ but also within idol industry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.4272248558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "この差を埋めるには……もっともっと徹底的に研究して\n練習するしかないと改めて思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To bridge this gap… I realized\nI need to study and practice more thoroughly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.1000017804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski023.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、いくら同じようにステップを踏んでも\nいくら資料を集めて研究しても……どこか違うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ no matter how similarly I follow their steps‚\nno matter how much I study and gather data… there's something different.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.0666735333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "私のダンスはどこか表面的で\n何か根本的なものが掴めていない気がして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like my dance lacks depth‚\nI don't think I'm grasping the basics‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.2000200909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski025.m4a",
      "text": "物真似だって、迷走しているように見えたかも\nしれませんが……ちゃんと本気なんですからね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and my imitation might have even seemed aimless…\nbut I'm serious about it‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.9000200909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで悩んでの物真似だった訳か。沙季、無理に\n今のまま行かなくても、まだ曲を変える時間はあるぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You went through all that trouble with your imitation. Saki‚\nThere's still time to change the song if you want.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.460146488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski026.m4a",
      "text": "今から曲を変える……\n……すみません、もう少しだけ……考えさせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Changing the song now…\n…I'm sorry‚ but please give me a little more time to think about it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 251.3000241598,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6566.6387555000365,
          "startTime": 257.8666629153
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――後日、帰り道",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――On the way to go back after this",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 256.4666588466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
