      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 269.548148693
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "……ダンス大会に強い想いで挑んでくれるのは嬉しい\nだけど、目の前の仕事に集中出来なければ本末転倒だぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's good to see you approaching the dance competition with such determination.\nBut if you can't focus on the tasks at hand‚ it's counterproductive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.5814942333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "今日だって、収録中にぼーっとしてただろ？\n沙季らしくないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even today‚ weren't you zoning out during the recording?\nIt's not like you‚ Saki.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 282.7481588655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 284.4481466585
    },
    {
