      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski028.m4a",
      "text": "それは……その、本当に、すみませんでした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm truly sorry… for that‚ really.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.4481466585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 290.3699887885
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "気を付けるように。それにしても、沙季はどうして\nそこまでスリクスの曲にこだわるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Be more mindful. But why are you\nso obsessed with IIIX's songs?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 294.5700009955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 297.4699786159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski029.m4a",
      "text": "私は……少しでも早く成長しないといけないんです\n今、月ストとサニピは明らかに差が開いています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… need to grow as quickly as possible.\nCurrently‚ there's a clear gap between Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 303.4333778381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski030.m4a",
      "text": "この差を覆すには、今自分が持っていないものを\n吸収するしかないと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To bridge this gap‚ I believe I need to absorb\nwhat I currently don't have.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 311.4667193095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 314.1215056075
    },
    {
