      "text": "一緒にデビューして頑張ってきたサニピに負けたくない\nそして何より……千紗に負けたくない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to lose to Sunny Peace‚ with whom I debuted together.\nAnd above all… I don't want to lose to Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 318.1667193095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
