      "text": "あの子に追いついて、一緒に輝きたいんです\n……{user}さん、率直に聞きます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to catch up to her and shine together.\n…{user}-san‚ I'll be straightforward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 328.3000445048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-ski033.m4a",
      "text": "私のダンス、どう思いますか？\n何かが足りない……そう思ってるんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think of my dancing?\nDo you feel like something's missing…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 335.3333920796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "そう……だな。確かに、沙季のダンスは悪くない\nだけど、そこで止まっている感じがする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… you're right. Your dancing is good‚\nbut it feels like you're stuck.",
